	(text "IF THE BOARD IS USE WITH AN ESP32 A LEVEL SHIFTER \nFOR THE I2C COMMUNICATION IS NEDDED.\n\nPULL UPS RESISTOR OF THE MAX5217 ARE CONNECTED TO 5V\nBECAUSE MAX5217 IS POWERED WITH 5V AND A HIGH LEVEL\nIS 0.7*VCC ~ 3.4 V SO 3.3V LOGIC CAN BE TRICKY AS IT\nMAY BE NOT ENOUGH.\nMAX 5217 NEEDS TO BE POWERED WITH 5V IN ORDER TO BE\n\nYOU MAY CONSIDERED ADDING A LEVEL SHIFTER TO THIS DESIGN OR USING AN EXTERNAL ONE.\nABLE TO GENERATE SIGNAL FROM 0 TO 5V AT THE OUTPUT."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 91.44 136.652 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
				(thickness 0.254)
				(bold yes)
				(color 255 6 0 1)
			)
		)
		(uuid "0b8e49ef-6345-4b1d-9bfb-b0e18c781baa")
	)
